Company Profile:We are a local mobile apps development
company that develops mobile apps that connect
people, create value, and simplify lives.  We are very keen on accepting
interns to work with us on our numerous
projects as mobile apps designers.  We will provide training and guidance
as well as offer interns allowances at $800/month.  Only the best need apply.  We will be
offering a total 4 internship positions at any time.  We are also prepared to hire the
outstanding interns after the internship.
Job Description:The mobile app designer will be responsible for creating design solutions for the assigned mobile app assuring that users will see a simple UI and the app will have a good UX.  He/she will be involved in the planning stage to ensure a full understanding of the features and functionality of the app
Please apply for this position by submitting your text CV using InternSG.
